commit.message: Export testVerifier results to image files
updated testVerifier with 2D data contour plot
Fixed errors in 2d simulation data generation
Separated config files for the 1d and 2d simulations
Added first complete test of verifier
Implemented upgradeMatrix, but requires more testing and should probably be made more efficient
added function to generate correct and corrupted data
Fixed derivs_needed in Parser to be a dictionary of the highest order derivative required instead of just a list of coordinate variables
Updated Parser.py to call, e.g., deriv['t'][3] instead of deriv['t'] @ deriv['t'] @ deriv['t']
